WEBVTT

00:06.480 --> 00:08.400
<i>[distant screaming]</i>

00:27.720 --> 00:28.560
<i>[groans]</i>

00:28.640 --> 00:30.440
<i>[head bounces, rolls]</i>

00:30.520 --> 00:32.200
<i>[dramatic music plays]</i>

00:43.080 --> 00:44.080
<i>[man] Your men,</i>

00:44.800 --> 00:47.720
<i>your ships, and your kingdom...</i>

00:49.000 --> 00:52.160
<i>now belong to Cumber the Ice King.</i>

00:55.280 --> 00:56.440
<i>Tell Uther,</i>

00:58.640 --> 01:00.560
<i>tell the King of Lies,</i>

01:00.960 --> 01:04.600
<i>the true blood heir to House Pendragon</i>
<i>has come!</i>

01:04.680 --> 01:07.040
<i>[cheering]</i>

01:13.560 --> 01:15.400
<i>[eerie ethereal music plays]</i>

02:13.920 --> 02:15.120
<i>[Lenore] </i>Listen to me.

02:15.520 --> 02:17.160
<i>It's all that matters now.</i>

02:17.240 --> 02:19.000
<i>Bring this to Merlin.</i>

02:19.080 --> 02:19.960
<i>It's all that matters.</i>

02:20.040 --> 02:21.640
<i>It's in your blood, child.</i>

02:30.880 --> 02:32.600
<i>-[Arthur] It's there.</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

02:35.400 --> 02:37.120
<i>I've, um, been guarding it.</i>

02:40.800 --> 02:43.800
<i>I'm actually rather relieved</i>
<i>you finally woke up.</i>

02:46.280 --> 02:47.520
<i>They don't like me here.</i>

02:48.480 --> 02:49.880
<i>You know, Man Blood and all.</i>

02:49.960 --> 02:50.960
<i>"Man Blood"?</i>

02:52.280 --> 02:53.160
<i>Non-Fey.</i>

02:55.240 --> 02:56.200
<i>Too human.</i>

02:57.000 --> 02:59.520
<i>And that I... I don't have antlers.</i>

02:59.920 --> 03:00.880
<i>Or wings.</i>

03:04.200 --> 03:05.040
<i>[Morgana] You're up.</i>

03:06.160 --> 03:07.120
<i>See?</i>

03:07.800 --> 03:08.960
<i>What did I tell you?</i>

03:09.040 --> 03:10.120
<i>[Morgana laughs]</i>

03:10.840 --> 03:11.840
<i>You're not alone.</i>

03:14.880 --> 03:16.040
<i>Welcome to Nemos.</i>

03:17.880 --> 03:18.720
<i>Dizier.</i>

03:20.080 --> 03:21.080
<i>I know.</i>

03:21.520 --> 03:22.360
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

03:22.440 --> 03:23.520
<i>I'm responsible.</i>

03:23.600 --> 03:26.000
<i>[Morgana] No. He understood the risks.</i>

03:26.360 --> 03:28.760
<i>Just honor his memory.</i>

03:39.760 --> 03:40.720
<i>Comfortable?</i>

03:42.280 --> 03:43.280
<i>We need hunters.</i>

03:43.640 --> 03:45.320
<i>Go make yourself useful, brother.</i>

03:50.280 --> 03:52.600
<i>[Nimue] Bring the sword to Merlin,</i>
<i>that's what she said.</i>

03:52.680 --> 03:56.000
<i>[Morgana] Merlin the Magician?</i>
<i>Counselor to King Uther Pendragon?</i>

03:56.080 --> 03:58.120
<i>-The same Merlin?</i>
<i>-I don't know.</i>

03:58.200 --> 04:00.800
<i>The only Merlin I know is</i>
<i>the one in the old legends.</i>

04:00.880 --> 04:02.720
<i>[Morgana] Yeah,</i>
<i>I'm told he's flesh and blood.</i>

04:02.920 --> 04:06.200
<i>Then it must be the same one.</i>
<i>But did your mother tell you why, or...</i>

04:06.280 --> 04:07.200
<i>[Nimue] Why him?</i>

04:07.560 --> 04:09.680
<i>She didn't. She never had the chance.</i>

04:09.760 --> 04:10.640
<i>Oh...</i>

04:11.240 --> 04:12.800
<i>I'm sorry, Nimue. I didn't...</i>

04:14.320 --> 04:18.200
<i>It's true. Merlin's a Druid and ancient,</i>
<i>if you believe the legends.</i>

04:18.280 --> 04:21.760
<i>He's no friend to the Fey, though.</i>
<i>His loyalty's to the kings of men.</i>

04:21.840 --> 04:23.200
<i>Are you sure he's the one?</i>

04:23.800 --> 04:25.600
<i>Mother must have known something</i>
<i>about him.</i>

04:25.680 --> 04:26.720
<i>[man] Caught one.</i>

04:26.800 --> 04:28.560
<i>-We need five more.</i>
<i>-[man grunts]</i>

04:31.280 --> 04:32.840
<i>[Morgana] And what about Arthur?</i>

04:35.080 --> 04:36.600
<i>It's complicated.</i>

04:37.400 --> 04:38.320
<i>He saved my life.</i>

04:38.400 --> 04:40.680
<i>But you wouldn't have been in</i>
<i>that situation if not for him.</i>

04:40.760 --> 04:43.520
<i>Yeah, but he didn't know</i>
<i>that the sword was... [sighs]</i>

04:44.000 --> 04:45.400
<i>Look, why am I defending him?</i>

04:45.760 --> 04:46.680
<i>You're his sister.</i>

04:46.760 --> 04:48.600
<i>[Morgana] Exactly. I know him best.</i>

04:48.680 --> 04:49.920
<i>And what does that mean?</i>

04:50.000 --> 04:53.000
<i>It means there's very little time</i>
<i>for little-girl crushes.</i>

04:53.760 --> 04:54.640
<i>What?</i>

04:55.120 --> 04:56.760
<i>That's ridiculous.</i>

04:56.840 --> 04:59.600
<i>You're far too important to tie your heart</i>
<i>to one man,</i>

05:00.280 --> 05:01.320
<i>to any man.</i>

05:01.400 --> 05:04.640
<i>You're not some Druid maid anymore, Nimue,</i>
<i>you're the Wolf-Blood Witch.</i>

05:04.960 --> 05:06.680
<i>You wield the Devil's Tooth.</i>

05:07.160 --> 05:10.640
<i>And unless you start to claim this fate,</i>
<i>it'll eat you alive.</i>

05:11.120 --> 05:13.600
<i>And it starts</i>
<i>with knowing who your true friends are.</i>

05:14.320 --> 05:16.680
<i>-And how do I know that?</i>
<i>-Well, look around you.</i>

05:17.840 --> 05:21.640
<i>When the paladins come for me,</i>
<i>no bards will sing my story.</i>

05:22.560 --> 05:24.280
<i>I've thrown my lot in</i>
<i>with these poor souls,</i>

05:24.360 --> 05:26.040
<i>and there is no turning back.</i>

05:26.520 --> 05:29.360
<i>Morgana, for that and more,</i>
<i>I welcome your friendship.</i>

05:31.840 --> 05:32.880
<i>Will you help me, then?</i>

05:33.680 --> 05:35.200
<i>Will you help me find Merlin?</i>

05:35.440 --> 05:36.400
<i>[Morgana] I will.</i>

05:36.480 --> 05:37.880
<i>But understand this, Nimue.</i>

05:38.440 --> 05:41.160
<i>You are in a far stronger position</i>
<i>than you realize.</i>

05:41.560 --> 05:44.760
<i>Every king from the Northlands to</i>
<i>the Southern Deserts will want this sword</i>

05:44.840 --> 05:47.520
<i>so they may proclaim themselves</i>
<i>the king of all kings.</i>

05:49.160 --> 05:51.640
<i>You're in a position</i>
<i>to bargain for your survival,</i>

05:52.240 --> 05:53.680
<i>for your people's survival.</i>

05:55.720 --> 05:57.000
<i>[horse brays, snorts]</i>

06:13.520 --> 06:14.720
<i>-[man 1] That him?</i>
<i>-[man 2] Yes.</i>

06:16.840 --> 06:17.840
<i>[man 3] Whoa.</i>

06:19.760 --> 06:21.240
<i>[man 1] Merlin the Magician?</i>

06:21.960 --> 06:23.800
<i>I was. Once.</i>

06:23.880 --> 06:27.200
<i>Well, whoever you are now,</i>
<i>you're under arrest.</i>

06:30.640 --> 06:31.840
<i>On what charge?</i>

06:32.120 --> 06:33.120
<i>[man 1] Treason.</i>

06:33.480 --> 06:34.840
<i>To His Majesty the King.</i>

06:37.600 --> 06:38.560
<i>Treason?</i>

06:39.520 --> 06:40.760
<i>To the Widow, my girl.</i>

06:40.840 --> 06:41.880
<i>Run like the wind.</i>

06:43.880 --> 06:45.080
<i>[man 1] Surround him!</i>

06:45.760 --> 06:47.160
<i>[tense music plays]</i>

06:53.400 --> 06:54.640
<i>[ominous music plays]</i>

06:55.040 --> 06:56.560
<i>[distant shouting]</i>

07:16.360 --> 07:17.200
<i>[Carden] Hold.</i>

07:20.640 --> 07:21.640
<i>It's all right.</i>

07:28.800 --> 07:30.240
<i>[water trickling]</i>

07:30.320 --> 07:32.160
<i>[man] Over here, Father.</i>

07:33.080 --> 07:34.160
<i>Your Holiness.</i>

07:34.800 --> 07:36.960
<i>Rise, Father Carden.</i>

07:37.880 --> 07:39.680
<i>And approach, please.</i>

07:42.440 --> 07:45.000
<i>[pope] I find these waters</i>
<i>very restorative.</i>

07:45.080 --> 07:47.960
<i>You must be tired after your long journey.</i>

07:48.040 --> 07:49.680
<i>Shall we draw you a bath?</i>

07:50.520 --> 07:53.160
<i>I doubt if I've used all the hot water.</i>

07:54.560 --> 07:57.760
<i>Please don't trouble yourself,</i>
<i>Your Holiness.</i>

07:57.840 --> 07:59.680
<i>No rest from the work, </i>

08:00.240 --> 08:01.560
<i>the Great Work.</i>

08:02.800 --> 08:06.640
<i>Your efforts have not gone unnoticed,</i>
<i>Father Carden, I assure you.</i>

08:08.160 --> 08:09.800
<i>How many villages...</i>

08:10.560 --> 08:12.600
<i>cleansed</i> so far, Father?

08:12.680 --> 08:13.680
<i>Is there a number?</i>

08:13.760 --> 08:17.160
<i>Some can hardly be called villages,</i>
<i>Your Holiness.</i>

08:18.120 --> 08:20.240
<i>Many live in trees like animals.</i>

08:20.760 --> 08:25.320
<i>Others live in tents made of skin</i>
<i>beneath the swamp water.</i>

08:25.800 --> 08:27.120
<i>Incredible.</i>

08:28.240 --> 08:29.680
<i>But we are rooting them out.</i>

08:30.320 --> 08:31.480
<i>Praise be to God.</i>

08:31.560 --> 08:33.880
<i>Glory be to God, indeed.</i>

08:35.640 --> 08:38.920
<i>How many Red Paladins do you command?</i>

08:39.000 --> 08:41.400
<i>We're overrun with volunteers,</i>
<i>Your Holiness.</i>

08:41.960 --> 08:43.720
<i>In some areas, we've lost count.</i>

08:44.440 --> 08:46.480
<i>However, it would not be boastful</i>

08:46.920 --> 08:49.320
<i>to suggest 5,000.</i>

08:51.240 --> 08:52.960
<i>That is impressive.</i>

08:53.840 --> 08:55.200
<i>And losses?</i>

08:57.560 --> 08:59.320
<i>-Some.</i>
<i>-Some?</i>

09:00.480 --> 09:02.200
<i>How much is "some"?</i>

09:02.280 --> 09:03.680
<i>We've encountered some...</i>

09:04.360 --> 09:06.920
<i>minor resistance in the hills near Cinder.</i>

09:08.880 --> 09:11.160
<i>[pope] Is this</i>
<i>what we're calling the "child"?</i>

09:11.240 --> 09:12.320
<i>A Resistance? </i>

09:12.400 --> 09:14.560
<i>-All by herself?</i>
<i>-She's not all by herself--</i>

09:14.640 --> 09:17.000
<i>Don't contradict me.</i>
<i>You said she was burned.</i>

09:17.400 --> 09:19.040
<i>To discourage her followers.</i>

09:19.120 --> 09:21.360
<i>Or to hide your failures from me.</i>

09:21.440 --> 09:23.560
<i>You're turning her into a symbol.</i>

09:24.360 --> 09:26.880
<i>You've already named her</i>
<i>the Wolf-Blood Witch.</i>

09:27.320 --> 09:30.200
<i>Perhaps you should pen a ballad</i>
<i>to her great deeds.</i>

09:31.240 --> 09:33.120
<i>We're setting a trap, Your Holiness.</i>

09:33.840 --> 09:35.320
<i>And when we find her,</i>

09:35.400 --> 09:40.200
<i>I swear by Almighty God</i>
<i>that I will make such an example of her,</i>

09:40.280 --> 09:42.920
<i>as will drive her followers to despair</i>
<i>and madness.</i>

09:43.000 --> 09:44.280
<i>I hope so, Father,</i>

09:44.840 --> 09:48.000
<i>or it is you</i>
<i>who shall be made the example.</i>

09:48.360 --> 09:49.840
<i>[tense music plays]</i>

09:52.800 --> 09:55.200
<i>Is there anything else</i>
<i>you would like to tell me?</i>

09:57.200 --> 10:00.000
<i>She wields the Devil's Tooth,</i>
<i>Your Holiness.</i>

10:00.920 --> 10:03.280
<i>The Church wants that sword.</i>

10:05.000 --> 10:06.360
<i>Of course, Your Holiness.</i>

10:06.440 --> 10:07.560
<i>Displease me again,</i>

10:08.440 --> 10:12.360
<i>and my Trinity will assume command</i>
<i>of your Red Paladin army.</i>

10:13.960 --> 10:15.520
<i>Be advised, Father,</i>

10:15.920 --> 10:18.640
<i>my Trinity have many Godly virtues.</i>

10:19.600 --> 10:21.760
<i>Mercy is not one of them.</i>

10:21.840 --> 10:23.400
<i>[ominous music plays]</i>

10:25.280 --> 10:27.920
<i>I understand, Your Holiness.</i>

10:34.040 --> 10:35.040
<i>Now go.</i>

10:46.640 --> 10:52.320
<i>This is your failure that brings me here</i>
<i>to be the subject of such humiliation.</i>

10:53.360 --> 10:54.480
<i>Have you no pride?</i>

10:54.560 --> 10:56.400
<i>The witch mocks us.</i>

10:58.240 --> 10:59.680
<i>But mark my words,</i>

11:01.240 --> 11:02.440
<i>if I burn,</i>

11:03.880 --> 11:05.320
<i>I'll not burn alone.</i>

11:07.600 --> 11:09.600
<i>[menacing chorus music plays]</i>

11:17.880 --> 11:19.720
<i>[menacing music continues]</i>

11:26.160 --> 11:28.040
<i>[birds screeching]</i>

11:32.480 --> 11:34.560
<i>-What do you want, boy?</i>
<i>-I'm a girl.</i>

11:34.920 --> 11:36.480
<i>-I want to join you...</i>
<i>-[snickers]</i>

11:36.560 --> 11:38.120
<i>...I want to be a Red Paladin.</i>

11:38.200 --> 11:40.360
<i>[chuckles] We don't take girls.</i>

11:40.440 --> 11:41.640
<i>Go home. Piss off.</i>

11:41.720 --> 11:44.200
<i>Speak for yourself. I take girls.</i>

11:45.240 --> 11:46.400
<i>I don't have a home.</i>

11:47.360 --> 11:49.440
<i>There was evil there, so I burned it out.</i>

11:50.760 --> 11:52.840
<i>Please. I want to be a Red Paladin.</i>

11:52.920 --> 11:54.480
<i>I told you, piss off.</i>

11:54.560 --> 11:57.080
<i>What do I need to do? Tell me.</i>

11:57.600 --> 12:00.040
<i>Bring us the head of the Wolf-Blood Witch.</i>

12:00.600 --> 12:02.080
<i>[paladin snickering]</i>

12:08.920 --> 12:10.280
<i>[Morgana] Here.</i>

12:11.280 --> 12:14.480
<i>-What's this?</i>
<i>-Your letter to Merlin. I changed it.</i>

12:14.560 --> 12:16.480
<i>You changed it? Why?</i>

12:16.560 --> 12:18.400
<i>[Morgana] It needed more strength.</i>

12:23.960 --> 12:27.680
<i>"To the Great Merlin,</i>
<i>greetings from the Wolf-Blood Witch."</i>

12:28.440 --> 12:29.600
<i>Is that my proper name now?</i>

12:30.040 --> 12:31.040
<i>Keep going.</i>

12:33.880 --> 12:36.960
<i>"By now, I trust you're aware</i>
<i>I possess the sword of the ancients</i>

12:37.040 --> 12:38.440
<i>known as the Devil's Tooth.</i>

12:38.840 --> 12:40.520
<i>I assure you</i>
<i>that Father Carden knows this,</i>

12:40.600 --> 12:43.280
<i>for many of his paladin</i>
<i>have felt the sting of its bite."</i>

12:43.360 --> 12:45.080
<i>[Arthur] You really intend to send that?</i>

12:45.440 --> 12:48.520
<i>-[Morgana] What's wrong with it?</i>
<i>-You don't win allies with threats.</i>

12:48.600 --> 12:51.440
<i>-Nor with stolen swords.</i>
<i>-[Arthur] What the hell do you know?</i>

12:52.760 --> 12:54.320
<i>Look, she's no expert.</i>

12:54.600 --> 12:56.440
<i>Truly are brother and sister.</i>

12:56.520 --> 12:58.440
<i>These men have to see you as an equal.</i>

12:58.520 --> 12:59.920
<i>All they respect is power.</i>

13:01.080 --> 13:01.920
<i>Keep reading.</i>

13:04.680 --> 13:07.920
<i>[Nimue] "Yet, what I seek most is an end</i>
<i>to this violence and peace for my kind.</i>

13:08.000 --> 13:10.120
<i>I propose an alliance, Great Merlin,</i>

13:10.200 --> 13:13.760
<i>and request you use your influence</i>
<i>with the king to quell this massacre.</i>

13:14.520 --> 13:17.680
<i>In return, I offer you the Devil's Tooth,</i>
<i>the Sword of Power,</i>

13:17.760 --> 13:19.880
<i>and trust you will use it</i>
<i>to restore the Fey</i>

13:19.960 --> 13:21.440
<i>to their lands and villages.</i>

13:21.520 --> 13:25.600
<i>Refuse me, and I will water all the fields</i>
<i>of your kingdom with paladin blood."</i>

13:25.680 --> 13:26.920
<i>I love that last bit.</i>

13:27.360 --> 13:28.680
<i>Yeah, I'm not saying that.</i>

13:28.760 --> 13:30.240
<i>That's the best part.</i>

13:30.840 --> 13:31.720
<i>Morgana.</i>

13:33.960 --> 13:34.960
<i>[Morgana scoffs]</i>

13:47.880 --> 13:50.520
<i>[viking 1] Yeah, yeah.</i>
<i>Ah, there's no coins.</i>

13:51.320 --> 13:53.200
<i>-[viking 2] Ah!</i>
<i>-[viking 1] Told ya!</i>

13:53.280 --> 13:54.960
<i>Throw it to the sea, I says.</i>

13:55.040 --> 13:56.280
<i>[Pym whimpers]</i>

14:03.040 --> 14:04.880
<i>Might need to throw this one back.</i>

14:05.400 --> 14:07.280
<i>No... no!</i>

14:07.760 --> 14:08.720
<i>Valuables?</i>

14:08.800 --> 14:09.640
<i>Nothing.</i>

14:09.720 --> 14:12.880
<i>Are you mad sneaking on this ship?</i>
<i>Do you know whose ship it is?</i>

14:12.960 --> 14:14.520
<i>-[whimpers]</i>
<i>-Nice hair, though.</i>

14:14.600 --> 14:16.760
<i>-Fey wear it long like that.</i>
<i>-I'm not Fey.</i>

14:17.160 --> 14:18.840
<i>-I'm not.</i>
<i>-[footsteps approaching]</i>

14:18.920 --> 14:20.960
<i>Fey are bad luck.</i>

14:25.960 --> 14:26.800
<i>[whimpers]</i>

14:30.240 --> 14:32.040
<i>-Drown her.</i>
<i>-No, no, no, please! Please! No!</i>

14:32.120 --> 14:33.800
<i>[raider] Aren't the Fey healers?</i>

14:36.160 --> 14:37.000
<i>I mean,</i>

14:37.520 --> 14:38.480
<i>if she's Fey,</i>

14:39.720 --> 14:41.600
<i>they know about herbs</i>
<i>and that sort of thing.</i>

14:41.680 --> 14:42.600
<i>But I'm not...</i>

14:43.920 --> 14:45.120
<i>Uh... I mean...</i>

14:45.800 --> 14:46.640
<i>I...</i>

14:47.040 --> 14:48.120
<i>am Fey?</i>

14:48.200 --> 14:49.680
<i>Well, which is it?</i>

14:49.760 --> 14:51.360
<i>[tense music plays]</i>

14:53.280 --> 14:54.640
<i>I am Fey.</i>

14:57.280 --> 14:58.200
<i>And a healer.</i>

14:58.280 --> 15:00.160
<i>A very well respected healer.</i>

15:00.240 --> 15:01.920
<i>I was the healer in my village...</i>

15:02.840 --> 15:04.680
<i>and several surrounding villages,</i>
<i>actually.</i>

15:06.920 --> 15:09.200
<i>-Never lost a patient.</i>
<i>-[viking 3] She lies.</i>

15:09.600 --> 15:10.680
<i>With Thrain gone,</i>

15:12.320 --> 15:13.240
<i>could we use her?</i>

15:24.000 --> 15:26.880
<i>There are slower deaths than drowning,</i>

15:27.840 --> 15:28.800
<i>I promise you.</i>

15:28.880 --> 15:32.160
<i>If the ale turns sour</i>
<i>or I find any dead birds on deck,</i>

15:32.240 --> 15:33.880
<i>I blame you. Understand?</i>

15:34.200 --> 15:36.320
<i>-Otherwise, you will heal my wounded.</i>
<i>-Yes, ma'am.</i>

15:36.400 --> 15:38.480
<i>That's captain, you Fey bitch!</i>

15:38.560 --> 15:39.480
<i>Sorry.</i>

15:42.160 --> 15:43.920
<i>I need my crew strong.</i>

15:44.000 --> 15:45.960
<i>You serve the Red Spear now...</i>

15:47.080 --> 15:49.320
<i>in her war against Cumber the Ice King.</i>

15:50.120 --> 15:51.120
<i>[gasps]</i>

15:53.400 --> 15:56.120
<i>[Morgana] Don't lie to her.</i>
<i>She can read your thoughts.</i>

15:56.400 --> 15:57.680
<i>Just give her the letter.</i>

15:58.000 --> 15:59.160
<i>You're scaring me.</i>

15:59.240 --> 16:01.080
<i>Yeva is a real sorceress.</i>

16:01.160 --> 16:03.080
<i>A Moon Wing elder and quite mad.</i>

16:03.560 --> 16:06.160
<i>If she turns on you, it's very dangerous.</i>

16:07.280 --> 16:09.440
<i>But she's our best chance</i>
<i>at finding Merlin.</i>

16:11.240 --> 16:12.280
<i>Through there.</i>

16:16.240 --> 16:18.400
<i>-You're not coming?</i>
<i>-No Man Blood permitted.</i>

16:20.080 --> 16:21.080
<i>[bird cawing]</i>

16:24.800 --> 16:26.440
<i>[ethereal music plays]</i>

16:38.920 --> 16:40.840
<i>-[Nimue] Hello?</i>
<i>-[roots creaking]</i>

16:42.760 --> 16:43.840
<i>[distant squealing]</i>

16:44.440 --> 16:45.520
<i>[distant hissing]</i>

16:46.000 --> 16:46.840
<i>Hello?</i>

16:48.720 --> 16:50.640
<i>[squealing, hissing]</i>

16:55.640 --> 16:57.720
<i>They have many questions about you.</i>

16:58.360 --> 17:00.040
<i>[high-pitched whistling]</i>

17:02.240 --> 17:04.120
<i>I was told you might be able to help me.</i>

17:05.600 --> 17:06.720
<i>[slurping]</i>

17:10.440 --> 17:11.600
<i>You smell wrong.</i>

17:12.440 --> 17:13.600
<i>What are you?</i>

17:13.680 --> 17:14.520
<i>Sky Folk.</i>

17:14.960 --> 17:16.640
<i>You don't smell like Sky Folk.</i>

17:17.640 --> 17:21.760
<i>My mother was high priestess of our clan.</i>
<i>My father was our healer.</i>

17:22.240 --> 17:23.120
<i>Hmm.</i>

17:26.640 --> 17:27.880
<i>[owls squawking]</i>

17:30.480 --> 17:32.480
<i>When you think of them, there is pain.</i>

17:32.560 --> 17:34.960
<i>This priestess and this healer.</i>

17:35.960 --> 17:37.360
<i>[growling, snarling]</i>

17:37.440 --> 17:38.680
<i>Jonah, she's your daughter.</i>

17:39.080 --> 17:41.760
<i>[Jonah] You know what she is!</i>
<i>Tell me the truth, Lenore!</i>

17:41.840 --> 17:44.480
<i>-I don't know what you're talking about.</i>
<i>-Papa, don't go.</i>

17:44.560 --> 17:45.400
<i>[gasps]</i>

17:45.480 --> 17:47.680
<i>Is this what your father feared,</i>
<i>these scars?</i>

17:47.760 --> 17:50.160
<i>-Just stop it.</i>
<i>-He was right to fear you.</i>

17:50.560 --> 17:52.560
<i>He was right to fear your blood.</i>

17:54.720 --> 17:55.600
<i>Please.</i>

17:55.680 --> 17:58.600
<i>I just wanna know</i>
<i>if you can send this message to Merlin.</i>

17:58.680 --> 18:00.360
<i>-[owl screeching]</i>
<i>-Merlin?</i>

18:01.160 --> 18:02.040
<i>[spits]</i>

18:02.600 --> 18:04.720
<i>I curse that traitor to his kind.</i>

18:06.280 --> 18:08.960
<i>-What do you want with him?</i>
<i>-The message is private.</i>

18:10.040 --> 18:12.760
<i>But it is of vital importance</i>
<i>to the survival of the Fey.</i>

18:14.600 --> 18:15.800
<i>I don't know where he is.</i>

18:18.800 --> 18:19.680
<i>[sighs]</i>

18:20.200 --> 18:21.560
<i>[bird screeching]</i>

18:28.800 --> 18:30.680
<i>But Marguerite can find anything.</i>

18:32.440 --> 18:33.560
<i>Even traitors.</i>

18:35.440 --> 18:36.920
<i>[wind howling]</i>

18:37.680 --> 18:41.320
<i>[Uther] And taken three ports,</i>
<i>Hastings, Grimsby, and Dover,</i>

18:41.400 --> 18:44.000
<i>and sank five of our ships! Our ships!</i>

18:44.080 --> 18:46.800
<i>Good Lord, I hope you didn't blubber on</i>
<i>like this down at court.</i>

18:46.880 --> 18:49.880
<i>And claims he is the true Pendragon king!</i>

18:50.520 --> 18:51.600
<i>The audacity.</i>

18:52.040 --> 18:54.680
<i>Is this an invasion? Are we at war?</i>

18:54.760 --> 18:58.320
<i>It's the pity of princes that no one ever</i>
<i>teaches them how to take a punch.</i>

18:58.400 --> 19:01.560
<i>Because when someone finally does,</i>
<i>they screech like pheasants.</i>

19:03.160 --> 19:06.360
<i>Cumber wants the Sword of Power,</i>
<i>and unlike some monarchs I could mention,</i>

19:06.440 --> 19:08.440
<i>he appears motivated to actually get it.</i>

19:08.520 --> 19:10.840
<i>Of course we want the bloody sword!</i>

19:10.920 --> 19:13.000
<i>And how is that working out for you?</i>

19:16.120 --> 19:17.600
<i>Where is Merlin, anyway?</i>

19:18.560 --> 19:20.200
<i>Chained in his quarters.</i>

19:21.440 --> 19:24.040
<i>-Let him rot.</i>
<i>-Well, that certainly won't do.</i>

19:24.480 --> 19:26.760
<i>A Merlin rotting is a Merlin plotting.</i>

19:27.560 --> 19:31.440
<i>What has Merlin to do with Cumber</i>
<i>and our burning ports?</i>

19:31.520 --> 19:34.200
<i>Your weakness.</i>
<i>That's what they have in common.</i>

19:34.280 --> 19:37.640
<i>And I hasten to add Father Carden</i>
<i>and his Red Paladins to the mix,</i>

19:37.720 --> 19:39.640
<i>who apparently</i>
<i>can march through your lands</i>

19:39.720 --> 19:41.480
<i>and burn villages with impunity.</i>

19:49.440 --> 19:50.880
<i>[flies buzzing]</i>

19:52.200 --> 19:53.400
<i>Are they all poisoned?</i>

19:54.960 --> 19:56.120
<i>Not all.</i>

20:01.800 --> 20:03.360
<i>What would you have us do?</i>

20:06.360 --> 20:08.000
<i>Be the damn king.</i>

20:09.360 --> 20:13.400
<i>Demonstrate to your court, your subjects,</i>
<i>and potential usurpers</i>

20:13.480 --> 20:15.880
<i>what happens to layabouts and traitors.</i>

20:16.320 --> 20:17.600
<i>Kill Merlin.</i>

20:21.280 --> 20:22.120
<i>Kill him?</i>

20:22.200 --> 20:23.040
<i>Publicly.</i>

20:23.520 --> 20:24.480
<i>Loudly.</i>

20:24.840 --> 20:27.200
<i>So that it rattles</i>
<i>in the Ice King's halls.</i>

20:28.480 --> 20:29.480
<i>It's dangerous.</i>

20:29.560 --> 20:30.560
<i>Even better.</i>

20:31.320 --> 20:34.080
<i>It will show there's more than silk</i>
<i>beneath those breeches.</i>

20:34.160 --> 20:35.160
<i>And after?</i>

20:35.240 --> 20:36.760
<i>Embrace the Church.</i>

20:36.840 --> 20:39.280
<i>Ally with the Red Paladins</i>
<i>against the Ice King</i>

20:39.360 --> 20:40.840
<i>and throw him back into the sea.</i>

20:41.600 --> 20:43.720
<i>It will be easy to claim the sword</i>

20:44.120 --> 20:47.040
<i>once there are no kings to resist you.</i>

20:50.480 --> 20:51.520
<i>Thank you, Mother.</i>

20:54.920 --> 20:55.960
<i>Always a pleasure.</i>

20:57.920 --> 21:00.320
<i>Indeed, Your Majesty.</i>

21:06.240 --> 21:08.560
<i>[Arthur] Come on,</i>
<i>it's just a little further.</i>

21:08.640 --> 21:09.720
<i>[Nimue] I can't see.</i>

21:09.800 --> 21:11.440
<i>[romantic music plays]</i>

21:12.400 --> 21:13.480
<i>Are we outside?</i>

21:14.880 --> 21:16.560
<i>Arthur, I don't like surprises.</i>

21:19.080 --> 21:19.960
<i>There we are.</i>

21:23.160 --> 21:24.160
<i>Oh...</i>

21:24.760 --> 21:28.280
<i>[Arthur] Morgana says</i>
<i>it's the best-kept secret in the caves.</i>

21:30.120 --> 21:31.080
<i>It's warm.</i>

21:33.400 --> 21:35.560
<i>The snowmelt</i>
<i>from the top of the mountain...</i>

21:36.440 --> 21:38.920
<i>heats up as it works through the rocks.</i>

21:42.360 --> 21:44.320
<i>[Arthur groans] Well?</i>

21:46.080 --> 21:47.360
<i>Oh, my God!</i>

21:47.440 --> 21:49.200
<i>Some warning, please.</i>

21:49.280 --> 21:51.720
<i>-[Arthur] What are you waiting for?</i>
<i>-[water splashes]</i>

21:51.800 --> 21:52.880
<i>Oh, God.</i>

21:53.440 --> 21:54.640
<i>Ooh! [chuckles]</i>

21:54.960 --> 21:56.080
<i>Feels good.</i>

21:57.240 --> 21:58.360
<i>Come on.</i>

21:58.440 --> 22:00.120
<i>Oh, I'm... I'm fine, thanks.</i>

22:00.720 --> 22:03.200
<i>I have seen a naked woman before.</i>

22:03.600 --> 22:05.600
<i>We're all very impressed.</i>

22:31.560 --> 22:32.520
<i>[Nimue winces]</i>

22:44.680 --> 22:45.840
<i>[water splashes]</i>

22:58.280 --> 23:00.200
<i>You don't have to hide them, you know.</i>

23:01.600 --> 23:02.640
<i>[Nimue] Hide what?</i>

23:04.680 --> 23:05.720
<i>We all have scars.</i>

23:08.520 --> 23:09.400
<i>Nimue.</i>

23:10.960 --> 23:12.080
<i>-No, it's fine.</i>
<i>-Nimue!</i>

23:12.160 --> 23:14.600
<i>-[Nimue] It's... it's fine. It's too hot.</i>
<i>-Look.</i>

23:14.680 --> 23:16.520
<i>Look. Look!</i>

23:20.680 --> 23:21.640
<i>[chuckles]</i>

23:22.160 --> 23:25.040
<i>When I was a boy,</i>
<i>I used to bet on rat races.</i>

23:25.560 --> 23:26.480
<i>Ah...</i>

23:26.960 --> 23:28.360
<i>My first race,</i>

23:29.240 --> 23:30.200
<i>my rat got scared,</i>

23:30.600 --> 23:33.560
<i>ran up my trouser leg,</i>
<i>tried to eat his way out.</i>

23:35.000 --> 23:37.760
<i>Now, the boys had a good laugh.</i>

23:39.120 --> 23:40.720
<i>And I ran home crying and,</i>

23:41.640 --> 23:43.800
<i>well, dancing with a rat in my trousers.</i>

23:43.880 --> 23:45.040
<i>[both laugh]</i>

23:49.720 --> 23:50.720
<i>What about that one?</i>

23:52.200 --> 23:53.120
<i>Oh, that.</i>

23:54.920 --> 23:56.520
<i>That's from the first man I ever killed.</i>

23:56.880 --> 23:59.320
<i>Yeah, he stuck me pretty good</i>
<i>before it was over.</i>

24:00.400 --> 24:01.400
<i>Who was he?</i>

24:06.000 --> 24:08.760
<i>He was one of the brutes</i>
<i>who killed my father.</i>

24:11.960 --> 24:14.080
<i>Or so I thought.</i>

24:15.760 --> 24:19.200
<i>Turns out,</i>
<i>I'd... pegged the wrong gang for it.</i>

24:20.080 --> 24:23.280
<i>And not that he was... some angel.</i>
<i>He wasn't that.</i>

24:23.360 --> 24:25.880
<i>But he'd... done me no wrong.</i>

24:27.480 --> 24:31.000
<i>I was just... young</i>

24:31.560 --> 24:32.600
<i>and drunk and...</i>

24:33.520 --> 24:34.400
<i>angry.</i>

24:34.960 --> 24:37.000
<i>You wanted justice for your father.</i>

24:37.080 --> 24:38.400
<i>There is no justice.</i>

24:39.680 --> 24:40.720
<i>You know, men... </i>

24:40.800 --> 24:43.520
<i>[chuckles sadly]</i>
<i>...men aren't built for it.</i>

24:44.080 --> 24:45.320
<i>And truth is, it...</i>

24:46.680 --> 24:49.520
<i>would've broken my father's heart</i>
<i>to know what I'd done to him.</i>

24:59.280 --> 25:00.200
<i>Thank you.</i>

25:01.600 --> 25:02.560
<i>For what?</i>

25:04.600 --> 25:05.640
<i>For telling me.</i>

25:28.640 --> 25:31.480
<i>Nimue, I... Nimue, I can't stay.</i>

25:33.360 --> 25:36.080
<i>I have debts to bad men.</i>
<i>And not just Bors.</i>

25:37.440 --> 25:38.640
<i>There are others.</i>

25:39.000 --> 25:41.440
<i>You don't need my problems too. I'm sorry.</i>

25:41.520 --> 25:44.080
<i>-Why are you doing this?</i>
<i>-You deserve someone good.</i>

25:44.160 --> 25:45.080
<i>[chuckles]</i>

25:45.520 --> 25:47.120
<i>Have I judged you?</i>

25:50.440 --> 25:52.560
<i>-Did I say something?</i>
<i>-No, it's... ah!</i>

25:52.640 --> 25:53.720
<i>I'll mess it up.</i>

25:54.520 --> 25:55.480
<i>All right?</i>

25:56.400 --> 25:58.840
<i>I have to go.</i>
<i>I don't want to see you hurt.</i>

25:58.920 --> 25:59.920
<i>[chuckles lightly]</i>

26:01.440 --> 26:02.440
<i>You won't.</i>

26:06.440 --> 26:07.280
<i>You'll be gone.</i>

26:15.000 --> 26:16.800
<i>[waves crashing]</i>

26:22.440 --> 26:24.200
<i>-[yelling]</i>
<i>-[screaming]</i>

26:35.480 --> 26:36.440
<i>What ails you?</i>

26:37.720 --> 26:38.720
<i>[viking grunts]</i>

26:38.800 --> 26:40.280
<i>Oh, my...</i>

26:42.120 --> 26:43.000
<i>[gasps]</i>

26:43.080 --> 26:45.520
<i>You mind cracking it in</i>
<i>so I can get back out there?</i>

26:48.000 --> 26:48.840
<i>What now?</i>

26:49.760 --> 26:52.400
<i>I've just been having dark thoughts</i>
<i>of late.</i>

26:55.320 --> 26:56.160
<i>Tell me.</i>

26:56.240 --> 26:57.240
<i>[groans]</i>

26:57.840 --> 26:59.560
<i>Thrain would've just cut them off!</i>

26:59.640 --> 27:01.720
<i>[Pym] Well, Thrain's dead!</i>
<i>You've got me now!</i>

27:01.800 --> 27:03.440
<i>[groans loudly]</i>

27:05.200 --> 27:06.160
<i>I got one.</i>

27:10.120 --> 27:11.320
<i>[sighs]</i>

27:13.840 --> 27:15.360
<i>[raider] How goes it, Minnow?</i>

27:18.120 --> 27:20.200
<i>Did you do this to me on purpose?</i>

27:23.480 --> 27:24.720
<i>I saved your life.</i>

27:25.320 --> 27:27.720
<i>[scoffs] Drowning would be a mercy.</i>

27:29.160 --> 27:31.240
<i>-[groans lightly]</i>
<i>-[raider] Does your stomach ail you?</i>

27:36.680 --> 27:37.560
<i>Here.</i>

27:39.040 --> 27:39.920
<i>Give your hand.</i>

27:45.000 --> 27:47.280
<i>Mm! Ow!</i>

27:49.600 --> 27:50.600
<i>Ow!</i>

27:51.040 --> 27:52.120
<i>You have blood on you.</i>

27:52.200 --> 27:54.840
<i>Yeah, I pulled out this arrow,</i>
<i>and there was just...</i>

27:55.360 --> 27:57.760
<i>[lip-trill] ...blood everywhere.</i>

28:03.040 --> 28:05.840
<i>Are you gonna keep pinching me or...</i>

28:08.040 --> 28:09.040
<i>Stomach better?</i>

28:09.800 --> 28:10.720
<i>Dunno.</i>

28:12.240 --> 28:14.440
<i>-Maybe.</i>
<i>-Never lost a patient.</i>

28:15.760 --> 28:17.680
<i>Look, are you injured? I'm very busy.</i>

28:17.760 --> 28:19.920
<i>I don't get injured on raids.</i>

28:21.320 --> 28:22.720
<i>Sigurd protects me.</i>

28:26.120 --> 28:28.360
<i>But if I can only see you</i>
<i>when I'm injured,</i>

28:29.880 --> 28:32.040
<i>perhaps I will leave Sigurd on board.</i>

28:33.320 --> 28:35.000
<i>[romantic music plays]</i>

28:35.960 --> 28:38.560
<i>[footsteps receding]</i>

28:40.120 --> 28:41.920
<i>[thunder cracking]</i>

28:44.040 --> 28:45.880
<i>[footsteps approaching]</i>

28:50.120 --> 28:51.160
<i>[door opens]</i>

28:54.360 --> 28:55.360
<i>Leave us.</i>

28:59.800 --> 29:00.800
<i>Your Highness.</i>

29:01.760 --> 29:02.840
<i>I would stand, but--</i>

29:02.920 --> 29:05.360
<i>Why didn't you tell us</i>
<i>about the Sword of the First Kings?</i>

29:06.480 --> 29:08.680
<i>-Well, I was--</i>
<i>-[Uther] Wait. We know.</i>

29:08.760 --> 29:13.800
<i>You wanted to acquire it for us first</i>
<i>before animating any false hopes.</i>

29:14.200 --> 29:15.680
<i>Well, yes, Your Majesty.</i>

29:15.760 --> 29:17.440
<i>Always the perfect answer.</i>

29:17.520 --> 29:20.720
<i>I confess, the way I left was not ideal,</i>

29:20.800 --> 29:22.120
<i>but you see, the omens--</i>

29:22.200 --> 29:24.160
<i>Yes, the omens.</i>

29:24.960 --> 29:27.400
<i>Blood raining down on Castle Pendragon.</i>

29:29.160 --> 29:30.880
<i>-Terrifying.</i>
<i>-Yes.</i>

29:32.200 --> 29:33.960
<i>But as I've said before,</i>
<i>there are different--</i>

29:34.040 --> 29:37.320
<i>Different possible meanings to signs.</i>
<i>Yes, we remember.</i>

29:39.720 --> 29:41.320
<i>We are not as stupid as you think.</i>

29:41.400 --> 29:44.600
<i>-I never suggested that--</i>
<i>-We remember all your lessons, Merlin.</i>

29:44.680 --> 29:47.480
<i>For instance, we need not fear omens,</i>

29:48.040 --> 29:49.680
<i>but rather we can seize them,</i>

29:49.760 --> 29:52.560
<i>turn them around, and examine them</i>

29:52.640 --> 29:54.320
<i>until they tell us something new.</i>

29:54.400 --> 29:56.520
<i>And then, through action,</i>

29:57.360 --> 29:59.600
<i>make those signs come true.</i>

30:01.440 --> 30:03.520
<i>And we found this thinking to be...</i>

30:04.440 --> 30:06.240
<i>particularly instructive.</i>

30:06.560 --> 30:07.520
<i>How so?</i>

30:07.600 --> 30:11.120
<i>Because we decided the blood</i>
<i>that fell upon the castle was not ours...</i>

30:13.160 --> 30:14.400
<i>-but yours.</i>
<i>-Uther!</i>

30:14.480 --> 30:18.120
<i>You never believed in us.</i>
<i>And now we no longer believe in you.</i>

30:19.600 --> 30:22.080
<i>The Age of Wizards is over, Merlin.</i>

30:23.160 --> 30:26.080
<i>We consider your recent derelictions</i>
<i>to be treason.</i>

30:26.160 --> 30:28.400
<i>And for that,</i>
<i>there can be only one recourse.</i>

30:32.040 --> 30:34.440
<i>-Execution.</i>
<i>-[Merlin] Without a trial?</i>

30:35.160 --> 30:36.400
<i>Without a hearing?</i>

30:37.080 --> 30:38.520
<i>Who's turned you against me?</i>

30:38.600 --> 30:41.400
<i>You've done that yourself</i>
<i>with your disdain for us,</i>

30:41.480 --> 30:42.600
<i>your drunkenness,</i>

30:42.680 --> 30:44.320
<i>and your disloyalty!</i>

30:47.400 --> 30:50.440
<i>You have every reason</i>
<i>to be disappointed in me, Uther.</i>

30:50.840 --> 30:52.840
<i>But if you want the Sword of Power,</i>

30:53.160 --> 30:54.960
<i>killing me is madness.</i>

30:55.440 --> 30:58.480
<i>See, I have it on good authority</i>
<i>the sword is coming to me.</i>

30:59.120 --> 31:00.280
<i>Now, give me one week--</i>

31:00.360 --> 31:01.280
<i>Oh, no.</i>

31:02.560 --> 31:04.920
<i>You have until the morning</i>
<i>to deliver the sword.</i>

31:06.520 --> 31:09.240
<i>And then we give the mob your head.</i>

31:10.040 --> 31:11.760
<i>What can I do from here, Uther?</i>

31:11.840 --> 31:13.800
<i>-That's not enough time.</i>
<i>-[door closes]</i>

31:14.360 --> 31:15.280
<i>Uther!</i>

31:15.600 --> 31:17.360
<i>-[tense music plays]</i>
<i>-[bird hooting]</i>

31:17.440 --> 31:18.800
<i>[sizzling]</i>

31:33.160 --> 31:34.080
<i>[distant grunting]</i>

31:34.160 --> 31:35.280
<i>[twigs snapping]</i>

31:36.960 --> 31:38.120
<i>[distant whispering]</i>

31:48.640 --> 31:49.840
<i>[Fey girl speaking Fey]</i>

31:50.320 --> 31:52.320
<i>[indistinct whispering]</i>

32:00.120 --> 32:03.000
<i>[Feys speaking Fey]</i>

32:09.120 --> 32:11.680
<i>[Fey girl, in English] Come with us.</i>
<i>We'll take you somewhere safe.</i>

32:15.080 --> 32:16.920
<i>[Fey kids sing] ♪ </i>In the ditch ♪

32:17.000 --> 32:21.640
<i>♪ Hiding from the Wolf-Blood Witch ♪</i>

32:22.200 --> 32:24.800
<i>♪ Paladin, paladin ♪</i>

32:24.880 --> 32:27.480
<i>♪ Choke and twitch ♪</i>

32:27.560 --> 32:33.200
<i>♪ Bitten by the Wolf-Blood Witch ♪</i>

32:33.560 --> 32:38.320
<i>♪ Paladin, paladin jump in the ditch ♪</i>

32:38.920 --> 32:43.600
<i>♪ Hiding from the Wolf-Blood Witch</i> <i>♪</i>

32:44.000 --> 32:46.160
<i>♪ Paladin, paladin...</i> <i>♪</i>

32:46.640 --> 32:47.680
<i>[speaking Fey]</i>

32:48.160 --> 32:50.080
<i>[in English]</i>
<i>Oh, no. Please, I want to be useful.</i>

32:50.160 --> 32:51.280
<i>[speaking Fey]</i>

32:52.680 --> 32:54.040
<i>[speaking Fey]</i>

32:54.560 --> 32:56.240
<i>[in English] I'm sorry, I don't, um...</i>

32:57.120 --> 32:58.360
<i>I don't understand.</i>

32:58.440 --> 33:00.200
<i>My name. Cora.</i>

33:00.280 --> 33:01.840
<i>Ah. Nimue.</i>

33:04.880 --> 33:07.360
<i>May I ask you,</i>
<i>do you know who's in this painting?</i>

33:08.320 --> 33:11.600
<i>The Green Knight is our leader,</i>
<i>our protector.</i>

33:12.000 --> 33:14.000
<i>He find the Fey to save them.</i>

33:14.400 --> 33:15.440
<i>The Green Knight.</i>

33:18.480 --> 33:20.560
<i>[Cora] Come. I show you something.</i>

33:24.640 --> 33:27.440
<i>Tomorrow night, there is </i>Amala.

33:27.520 --> 33:28.520
<i>A "Joining."</i>

33:29.920 --> 33:31.480
<i>No, I-- I can't.</i>

33:32.720 --> 33:34.640
<i>Not for me.</i> <i>You do too much.</i>

33:35.200 --> 33:36.840
<i>Yes, you will wear.</i>

33:37.280 --> 33:40.880
<i>You will come.</i>
<i>You and that handsome human boy.</i>

33:40.960 --> 33:42.360
<i>[girls giggle]</i>

33:43.320 --> 33:44.640
<i>[indistinct yelling]</i>

33:50.400 --> 33:51.560
<i>[booing]</i>

33:55.720 --> 33:58.800
<i>Your Majesty, without me,</i>
<i>you'll never get the Sword of Power.</i>

33:58.880 --> 34:00.400
<i>Our ears tire of your words.</i>

34:00.480 --> 34:01.320
<i>Uther!</i>

34:01.400 --> 34:02.400
<i>[shouts of encouragement]</i>

34:02.800 --> 34:03.800
<i>[Merlin] Uther!</i>

34:07.480 --> 34:08.400
<i>Uther!</i>

34:09.840 --> 34:11.600
<i>[crowd stops yelling]</i>

34:11.680 --> 34:14.400
<i>By the power invested in us</i>
<i>by Almighty God,</i>

34:15.400 --> 34:17.640
<i>Merlin the Magician,</i>
<i>you are hereby sentenced to die</i>

34:17.720 --> 34:21.000
<i>for the crime of treason</i>
<i>against our person.</i>

34:21.640 --> 34:23.080
<i>[tense music plays]</i>

34:28.160 --> 34:29.560
<i>-[Merlin yells]</i>
<i>-[bird screeching]</i>

34:29.640 --> 34:31.320
<i>[crowd exclaims]</i>

34:31.400 --> 34:33.600
<i>[dramatic music plays]</i>

34:35.640 --> 34:36.960
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

34:37.040 --> 34:37.960
<i>[screeches]</i>

34:38.760 --> 34:40.040
<i>A message, my liege.</i>

34:40.120 --> 34:41.480
<i>There is a note, sire.</i>

34:54.960 --> 34:55.800
<i>Well?</i>

34:56.880 --> 34:58.200
<i>Borley, what does it say?</i>

34:58.280 --> 35:01.960
<i>It is a letter from the Wolf-Blood Witch</i>
<i>offering to bring the Sword of Power,</i>

35:02.640 --> 35:04.240
<i>the Sword of the First Kings...</i>

35:05.800 --> 35:07.120
<i>to Merlin the Magician.</i>

35:07.200 --> 35:09.160
<i>Tell her I'm indisposed.</i>

35:09.240 --> 35:11.240
<i>[indistinct muttering from crowd]</i>

35:15.200 --> 35:17.000
<i>Get him up. Get him up!</i>

35:17.480 --> 35:20.240
<i>-Clean him up, then bring him before us.</i>
<i>-[crowd grumbles]</i>

35:20.320 --> 35:23.280
<i>-[crowd boos]</i>
<i>-You're one of Yeva's, are you?</i>

35:23.960 --> 35:26.720
<i>Tell that old crone</i>
<i>this changes nothing between us.</i>

35:26.800 --> 35:27.640
<i>[grunts]</i>

35:27.720 --> 35:30.040
<i>[dissatisfied yelling]</i>

35:32.640 --> 35:35.320
<i>[kids laughing, chattering in distance]</i>

35:40.680 --> 35:42.200
<i>[man] That's the best part.</i>

35:44.200 --> 35:45.120
<i>There you are.</i>

35:51.000 --> 35:52.000
<i>[Arthur] Nimue?</i>

35:52.080 --> 35:52.960
<i>Yes?</i>

35:55.360 --> 35:56.480
<i>[sighs] Oh.</i>

35:57.040 --> 35:58.520
<i>There's a Joining tonight.</i>

35:59.600 --> 36:00.760
<i>Like your weddings.</i>

36:01.600 --> 36:03.680
<i>They, uh... made me this.</i>

36:05.200 --> 36:06.600
<i>Yeah, you look like a dream.</i>

36:08.880 --> 36:10.000
<i>You're leaving now?</i>

36:12.400 --> 36:13.320
<i>Yes.</i>

36:14.880 --> 36:15.840
<i>I, um...</i>

36:20.400 --> 36:22.160
<i>I'll never be what my father hoped.</i>

36:23.800 --> 36:25.640
<i>I'll-- I'll never be a true knight.</i>

36:27.480 --> 36:29.480
<i>But maybe somewhere I can find my honor.</i>

36:30.480 --> 36:33.320
<i>Maybe somewhere I can find... justice.</i>

36:35.360 --> 36:37.560
<i>Are you searching or just running away?</i>

36:39.320 --> 36:41.200
<i>They can look the same, you know.</i>

36:41.280 --> 36:42.280
<i>Honestly, I'm...</i>

36:43.880 --> 36:44.960
<i>I don't know anymore.</i>

36:47.720 --> 36:48.960
<i>You'll ride through the night?</i>

36:49.320 --> 36:51.360
<i>With everyone looking for me,</i>
<i>I thought it best.</i>

36:53.400 --> 36:54.400
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

36:55.040 --> 36:56.440
<i>I-- I-- I wish we could ju--</i>

37:00.840 --> 37:01.880
<i>No. Forget it.</i>

37:04.400 --> 37:05.840
<i>Come with me to the Joining.</i>

37:07.760 --> 37:10.960
<i>I mean, wouldn't it be lovely</i>
<i>just to forget it all for an hour?</i>

37:12.320 --> 37:14.480
<i>No swords or debts or...</i>

37:15.240 --> 37:16.440
<i>Merlins or paladins.</i>

37:16.520 --> 37:17.440
<i>We could just...</i>

37:18.480 --> 37:19.360
<i>be us.</i>

37:21.360 --> 37:22.760
<i>I would like that very much.</i>

37:22.840 --> 37:23.800
<i>Would you?</i>

37:25.440 --> 37:26.600
<i>-Well...</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

37:27.600 --> 37:28.600
<i>[laughs gently]</i>

37:29.640 --> 37:31.680
<i>Well, all right, then.</i>

37:32.440 --> 37:34.520
<i>[folk music plays]</i>

37:34.640 --> 37:38.000
<i>[Fey folk laughing, chattering, cheering]</i>

37:38.080 --> 37:39.160
<i>[chuckling]</i>

37:52.480 --> 37:54.760
<i>[band continues playing folk music]</i>

38:09.480 --> 38:10.800
<i>[Fey folk cheering]</i>

38:16.000 --> 38:17.360
<i>[Fey man whooping]</i>

38:23.200 --> 38:24.560
<i>[rhythmic clapping]</i>

38:26.880 --> 38:28.480
<i>-[whooping]</i>
<i>-[laughter]</i>

38:28.880 --> 38:29.840
<i>[woman] Whey!</i>

38:30.720 --> 38:32.720
<i>[band continues playing folk music]</i>

39:02.240 --> 39:03.280
<i>[whooping]</i>

39:13.280 --> 39:14.440
<i>[whooping]</i>

39:17.480 --> 39:18.480
<i>[Nimue giggles]</i>

39:20.040 --> 39:21.920
<i>[folk music fades]</i>

39:24.520 --> 39:25.960
<i>[romantic music plays]</i>

39:33.080 --> 39:34.840
<i>[romantic music intensifies]</i>

39:44.200 --> 39:45.160
<i>Nimue...</i>

39:46.680 --> 39:47.640
<i>what if it's you?</i>

39:48.440 --> 39:49.600
<i>What if what's me?</i>

39:49.680 --> 39:51.000
<i>What if you're my honor?</i>

39:52.000 --> 39:54.160
<i>What if it's your justice</i>
<i>I'm meant to serve?</i>

39:57.120 --> 39:59.400
<i>Your honor was never lost, Arthur.</i>

40:02.480 --> 40:04.080
<i>But if you want to stay,</i>

40:06.800 --> 40:07.960
<i>I want you to stay.</i>

40:12.320 --> 40:13.440
<i>[muffled cheering]</i>

40:13.520 --> 40:15.360
<i>[Fey folk exclaim excitedly]</i>
<i>The Green Knight!</i>

40:15.440 --> 40:16.800
<i>-The Green Knight is here.</i>
<i>-The who?</i>

40:16.880 --> 40:19.160
<i>-[man 1] The Green Knight!</i>
<i>-[man 2] Spread the word, child!</i>

40:20.640 --> 40:22.200
<i>-Come on.</i>
<i>-[man 1] It's the Green Knight!</i>

40:22.280 --> 40:24.080
<i>Let's go see this Green Knight, then.</i>

40:25.000 --> 40:26.400
<i>[cheering, whooping]</i>

40:41.960 --> 40:42.920
<i>Squirrel?</i>

40:44.280 --> 40:45.720
<i>-Nimue!</i>
<i>-[Nimue] Oh!</i>

40:45.800 --> 40:47.280
<i>[relieved gasping]</i>

40:49.000 --> 40:52.120
<i>I... Thank the gods.</i>
<i>I... I looked for you.</i>

40:52.200 --> 40:53.320
<i>I'm sorry, Nimue.</i>

40:54.200 --> 40:55.280
<i>I heard you, but...</i>

40:55.880 --> 40:58.160
<i>You're here. It's okay. [giggles]</i>

40:58.880 --> 40:59.840
<i>You're here.</i>

41:00.680 --> 41:01.720
<i>You're alive!</i>

41:02.720 --> 41:03.680
<i>Oh!</i>

41:09.280 --> 41:11.000
<i>The Green Knight saved me.</i>

41:20.520 --> 41:21.360
<i>Gawain?</i>

41:21.440 --> 41:23.440
<i>[epic music swells]</i>

41:26.120 --> 41:27.040
<i>Nimue.</i>

41:29.640 --> 41:31.520
<i>-It's me. [Nimue shrieks]</i>
<i>-[giggles]</i>

41:31.600 --> 41:32.760
<i>[Nimue giggles]</i>

41:33.280 --> 41:35.120
<i>-Oh, my goodness.</i>
<i>-I can't believe you're alive.</i>

41:35.200 --> 41:37.640
<i>-I can't believe </i>you're <i>alive!</i>
<i>-I thought... Tell me everything.</i>

41:37.720 --> 41:39.440
<i>You need to tell the story...</i>

41:41.920 --> 41:44.920
<i>-[tense music plays]</i>
<i>-Don't be sad. You'll have friends here.</i>

41:46.680 --> 41:48.040
<i>This Man Blood smell funny.</i>

41:48.520 --> 41:49.600
<i>[girl] Don't be mean.</i>

41:50.520 --> 41:51.400
<i>You're safe.</i>

41:52.200 --> 41:53.240
<i>Because, look,</i>

41:54.880 --> 41:56.440
<i>the Wolf-Blood Witch is here.</i>

41:58.080 --> 42:00.280
<i>She kills all the Red Paladins.</i>

42:00.600 --> 42:02.800
<i>[Nimue] ...desiccated. How are you here?</i>

42:02.880 --> 42:04.400
<i>[ominous music plays]</i>

42:05.480 --> 42:06.960
<i>-I can't believe you're here.</i>
<i>-I can't.</i>

42:07.040 --> 42:08.960
<i>-I need to hear.</i>
<i>-You look so different.</i>

42:09.040 --> 42:11.200
<i>-It's just so...</i>
<i>-[Nimue] Well, it's been years.</i>

42:11.840 --> 42:13.240
<i>I... Um...</i>

42:13.640 --> 42:15.920
<i>Oh, Arthur, uh, this is Gawain.</i>

42:16.000 --> 42:17.000
<i>He's my, uh...</i>

42:17.640 --> 42:20.080
<i>He's like family,</i>
<i>one of my dearest, oldest friends.</i>

42:20.160 --> 42:21.120
<i>How nice.</i>

42:21.680 --> 42:23.360
<i>Gawain, this is Arthur.</i>

42:23.440 --> 42:25.920
<i>We're... friends?</i>

42:26.000 --> 42:28.440
<i>[giggles]</i>
<i>Kind of hard to describe what we are,</i>

42:28.520 --> 42:30.560
<i>but we've been on</i>
<i>quite the journey together.</i>

42:31.400 --> 42:32.480
<i>Arthur.</i>

42:35.080 --> 42:36.120
<i>Sell-sword?</i>

42:36.440 --> 42:37.280
<i>On occasion.</i>

42:37.640 --> 42:38.480
<i>Human.</i>

42:39.360 --> 42:40.600
<i>Uh... Aye.</i>

42:42.880 --> 42:45.080
<i>Thank you for taking care of my Nimue.</i>

42:46.440 --> 42:49.920
<i>Take as long as you need to rest up here.</i>
<i>What little we have, we will share.</i>

42:51.320 --> 42:52.240
<i>Thank you.</i>

42:55.120 --> 42:57.080
<i>We'll be right back. We just need...</i>

42:57.800 --> 43:00.320
<i>We have so much to catch up on,</i>
<i>but we'll...</i>

43:01.120 --> 43:03.520
<i>-I'll be right back, I promise.</i>
<i>-Take your time.</i>

43:12.880 --> 43:14.080
<i>[knocking at door]</i>

43:14.600 --> 43:15.680
<i>What is it?</i>

43:16.320 --> 43:17.360
<i>[flies buzzing]</i>

43:22.920 --> 43:23.840
<i>Merlin.</i>

43:25.440 --> 43:28.160
<i>-What a surprise.</i>
<i>-[Merlin] Your Majesty Queen Regent.</i>

43:28.600 --> 43:33.160
<i>To what do we owe the honor of your visit?</i>
<i>And may we offer you a cake?</i>

43:34.920 --> 43:36.080
<i>So kind of you.</i>

43:36.760 --> 43:38.400
<i>But I ate my fill at the court.</i>

43:39.440 --> 43:41.200
<i>Though I hear they are delightful.</i>

43:41.280 --> 43:42.280
<i>Wine, then?</i>

43:43.080 --> 43:46.000
<i>You must have earned quite a thirst</i>
<i>after such an exciting day.</i>

43:46.080 --> 43:47.240
<i>[laughs]</i>

43:49.440 --> 43:51.560
<i>Exciting day, yes.</i>

43:54.480 --> 43:57.280
<i>For some reason,</i>
<i>a day like this reminds me of a story.</i>

43:58.320 --> 43:59.640
<i>Perhaps you've heard it.</i>

44:00.240 --> 44:03.200
<i>Among the gentry,</i>
<i>they call it "The Story of the Midwife."</i>

44:03.880 --> 44:04.960
<i>I don't believe I have.</i>

44:05.960 --> 44:06.840
<i>Huh!</i>

44:09.360 --> 44:12.360
<i>They say it was an unusually cold night</i>
<i>for May.</i>

44:12.440 --> 44:14.560
<i>A frost had settled over the crops.</i>

44:15.040 --> 44:18.680
<i>And yet the people stood beneath the stars</i>
<i>holding candles</i>

44:19.120 --> 44:22.160
<i>because a king was being born that night.</i>

44:22.880 --> 44:24.240
<i>And this was very important</i>

44:24.320 --> 44:26.680
<i>because the king had died</i>
<i>only months before,</i>

44:26.760 --> 44:28.320
<i>leaving the queen a regent,</i>

44:28.680 --> 44:30.480
<i>not a true blood heir to the throne.</i>

44:31.120 --> 44:35.200
<i>[Merlin] </i>But were she to deliver a son,
then he would rule as the true king.

44:35.280 --> 44:37.040
<i>[woman screaming in pain]</i>

44:37.120 --> 44:38.400
<i>But as the night wore on,</i>

44:38.480 --> 44:41.240
<i>it became clear</i>
<i>that the child hadn't turned</i>

44:42.000 --> 44:44.480
<i>and struggled inside the Queen Regent.</i>

44:44.920 --> 44:48.160
<i>And though she prayed to St. Margaret</i>
<i>that her child come free</i>

44:48.240 --> 44:50.920
<i>as easily as Margaret escaped</i>
<i>the dragon's stomach...</i>

44:52.360 --> 44:53.920
<i>the baby was stillborn.</i>

44:55.880 --> 44:56.880
<i>And a boy.</i>

45:03.120 --> 45:06.240
<i>Knowing the dead child would snuff out</i>
<i>her claim to the throne,</i>

45:06.320 --> 45:09.840
<i>the Queen Regent huddled with the midwife</i>
<i>and devised a plot.</i>

45:10.680 --> 45:11.760
<i>And so...</i>

45:12.960 --> 45:14.400
<i>by the light of the moon...</i>

45:14.480 --> 45:15.440
<i>[wind howling]</i>

45:15.520 --> 45:19.600
<i>...the midwife snuck away from the castle</i>
<i>to a peasant's home that was known to her,</i>

45:20.280 --> 45:23.160
<i>one that had recently celebrated</i>
<i>the birth of a baby boy.</i>

45:25.680 --> 45:30.240
<i>It's said the mother was paid handsomely</i>
<i>in gold coins from the royal coffers.</i>

45:30.320 --> 45:31.400
<i>And yet...</i>

45:32.760 --> 45:33.880
<i>days later,</i>

45:35.120 --> 45:38.480
<i>the same woman was found dead</i>
<i>from a curious suffocation.</i>

45:39.400 --> 45:40.280
<i>[sniffs]</i>

45:40.960 --> 45:42.640
<i>Poisoned, some surmised.</i>

45:43.880 --> 45:48.000
<i>Indeed, almost anyone who might have known</i>
<i>of the foul conspiracy met similar ends.</i>

45:48.520 --> 45:50.880
<i>All except for the midwife,</i>

45:51.800 --> 45:53.920
<i>who, fearing for her life,</i>

45:54.000 --> 45:55.960
<i>fled the kingdom, never to return.</i>

45:57.160 --> 45:58.840
<i>One imagines were she ever found,</i>

45:58.920 --> 46:01.240
<i>she would represent quite a danger</i>
<i>to the king.</i>

46:02.280 --> 46:05.360
<i>Which I suspect is why</i>
<i>she remained hidden forever,</i>

46:05.440 --> 46:08.440
<i>given the grim outcomes</i>
<i>of the other characters in the story.</i>

46:08.520 --> 46:10.680
<i>Or perhaps the simpler explanation</i>

46:10.760 --> 46:13.640
<i>is that she never made it out</i>
<i>of the kingdom at all</i>

46:13.720 --> 46:19.240
<i>and shared the fate of that poor mother</i>
<i>who sold her child for a few gold coins.</i>

46:19.320 --> 46:21.600
<i>[Merlin]</i>
<i>That's always been my suspicion as well.</i>

46:22.200 --> 46:24.560
<i>-There is a third option, of course.</i>
<i>-Is there?</i>

46:24.960 --> 46:28.680
<i>That perhaps the midwife is alive and well</i>
<i>and under my protection.</i>

46:31.680 --> 46:32.760
<i>[knocks on door]</i>

46:34.080 --> 46:35.400
<i>Good night, Your Majesty.</i>

46:36.600 --> 46:38.040
<i>[footsteps receding]</i>

46:39.160 --> 46:42.040
<i>-[dramatic music plays]</i>
<i>-[indistinct yelling]</i>

46:48.280 --> 46:49.400
<i>[music stops]</i>

46:56.640 --> 46:58.160
<i>[mystical twinkling]</i>

47:09.520 --> 47:11.040
<i>[Gawain] Who knows about this?</i>

47:11.120 --> 47:12.080
<i>No one.</i>

47:13.920 --> 47:15.720
<i>Arthur knows and Morgana.</i>

47:15.800 --> 47:17.400
<i>Any of the Fey Elders?</i>

47:17.480 --> 47:18.320
<i>No.</i>

47:20.240 --> 47:21.080
<i>Why?</i>

47:25.000 --> 47:28.440
<i>[Gawain] This is the sword</i>
<i>of our people, Nimue.</i>

47:30.360 --> 47:32.320
<i>This is our history.</i>

47:34.480 --> 47:35.480
<i>Our hope.</i>

47:38.760 --> 47:41.920
<i>And you want to give this</i>
<i>to Merlin the Magician,</i>

47:43.280 --> 47:45.040
<i>who turned against his own kind?</i>

47:45.480 --> 47:48.240
<i>He's a conjurer</i>
<i>who serves a Man-Blood king.</i>

47:51.600 --> 47:54.840
<i>-[Nimue] It was Lenore's wish.</i>
<i>-I loved Lenore like my own mother.</i>

47:54.920 --> 47:55.880
<i>But this is wrong.</i>

47:55.960 --> 47:56.960
<i>Why him?</i>

47:58.000 --> 47:59.880
<i>-I don't know.</i>
<i>-Well, there must be a reason.</i>

48:00.280 --> 48:03.000
<i>Gawain, these were the very last words</i>
<i>she spoke to me.</i>

48:05.120 --> 48:07.680
<i>She could have said anything,</i>
<i>but she chose this:</i>

48:08.280 --> 48:09.960
<i>"Bring this to Merlin."</i>

48:11.520 --> 48:12.760
<i>A bargaining chip, then.</i>

48:13.800 --> 48:16.000
<i>She hoped</i>
<i>that this Merlin might protect you,</i>

48:16.080 --> 48:18.240
<i>but you don't need that</i>
<i>because I'll protect you.</i>

48:19.360 --> 48:21.240
<i>There is more to it. I know there is.</i>

48:24.160 --> 48:26.240
<i>-And I don't need protecting.</i>
<i>-[scoffs]</i>

48:27.160 --> 48:28.120
<i>Are you sure?</i>

48:30.080 --> 48:33.320
<i>This is also known</i>
<i>as the Sword of the First Kings.</i>

48:33.400 --> 48:34.720
<i>[mystical twinkling]</i>

48:35.280 --> 48:37.560
<i>[Gawain]</i>
<i>Uther Pendragon will want this sword.</i>

48:37.640 --> 48:41.040
<i>And if history is any guide,</i>
<i>then he will promise the world</i>

48:41.720 --> 48:44.960
<i>and then leave the Fey</i>
<i>at the mercy of the Red Paladins.</i>

48:46.520 --> 48:48.520
<i>Well, I wouldn't know, for I am no king.</i>

48:48.600 --> 48:50.000
<i>Then give it to someone else.</i>

48:51.320 --> 48:52.320
<i>Someone here.</i>

48:54.440 --> 48:56.120
<i>I will take it if I must,</i>

48:57.640 --> 48:58.640
<i>but not Merlin.</i>

48:59.360 --> 49:01.920
<i>Mother wouldn't be careless</i>
<i>about something like this.</i>

49:03.920 --> 49:05.280
<i>She wouldn't entrust...</i>

49:10.680 --> 49:11.680
<i>She knew him.</i>

49:13.360 --> 49:14.200
<i>How?</i>

49:14.280 --> 49:16.600
<i>I don't know,</i>
<i>but it's the only explanation.</i>

49:18.400 --> 49:19.640
<i>[Morgana sobs] Oh, no!</i>

49:20.680 --> 49:21.560
<i>No!</i>

49:22.920 --> 49:24.120
<i>[wailing sobs]</i>

49:26.480 --> 49:28.600
<i>-[woman] Morgana...</i>
<i>-[Morgana sobs]</i>

49:28.680 --> 49:30.360
<i>...it'll be all right. I promise.</i>

49:30.440 --> 49:31.840
<i>[Morgana] Get away from me!</i>

49:32.800 --> 49:34.200
<i>[sobbing]</i>

49:35.040 --> 49:36.280
<i>[Nimue] What's happened?</i>

49:37.560 --> 49:38.560
<i>There was word.</i>

49:40.880 --> 49:43.480
<i>-Yvoire Abbey is burned to the ground.</i>
<i>-[sobbing]</i>

49:46.560 --> 49:47.720
<i>Celia?</i>

49:48.600 --> 49:50.400
<i>-[Morgana cries]</i>
<i>-No survivors.</i>

49:52.440 --> 49:54.600
<i>-[Fey folk whisper]</i>
<i>-[tense music plays]</i>

50:00.280 --> 50:02.360
<i>-[distant bell tolling]</i>
<i>-[fire crackling]</i>

50:02.440 --> 50:04.120
<i>[nuns screaming]</i>

50:10.080 --> 50:12.760
<i>She must have been so afraid.</i>

50:16.120 --> 50:18.080
<i>Celia saw the good in everyone.</i>

50:19.840 --> 50:20.880
<i>Oh... [sobs]</i>

50:22.200 --> 50:24.480
<i>I have such hate in my heart.</i>

50:26.280 --> 50:28.440
<i>[sniffles] Such frightening hate.</i>

50:36.920 --> 50:39.040
<i>I guess we're both orphans now, aren't we?</i>

50:39.560 --> 50:40.720
<i>In a sense.</i>

50:41.320 --> 50:42.240
<i>I suppose we are.</i>

50:42.320 --> 50:43.400
<i>Sisters in blood.</i>

50:44.480 --> 50:45.880
<i>[wind howling]</i>

50:51.240 --> 50:52.760
<i>The traitor... [spits]</i>

50:53.520 --> 50:54.800
<i>...has given his answer.</i>

50:56.200 --> 50:57.520
<i>[high-pitched whistling]</i>

51:00.520 --> 51:02.160
<i>That lazy dog gives me work.</i>

51:02.520 --> 51:05.440
<i>Next time,</i>
<i>Marguerite brings back his balls.</i>

51:08.880 --> 51:12.040
<i>-[bird screeching]</i>
<i>-[chants incantation in Fey]</i>

51:21.080 --> 51:22.120
<i>What will happen?</i>

51:25.560 --> 51:28.120
<i>You sit, you breathe, you dream.</i>

51:29.240 --> 51:30.760
<i>The Hidden take you to Merlin.</i>

51:30.840 --> 51:32.960
<i>Not safe, he says, on the road.</i>

51:33.040 --> 51:35.120
<i>This is the way, the Old Druid way.</i>

51:39.880 --> 51:41.120
<i>Memory will come.</i>

51:42.040 --> 51:43.920
<i>Maybe good, maybe bad.</i>

51:44.480 --> 51:45.480
<i>Pay attention.</i>

51:45.880 --> 51:47.520
<i>That is the voice of the Hidden.</i>

51:48.200 --> 51:51.040
<i>And that is the road to the Between...</i>

51:51.960 --> 51:53.800
<i>where Merlin awaits you.</i>

51:54.400 --> 51:55.480
<i>[bird screeching]</i>

51:58.360 --> 51:59.680
<i>[chanting in Fey]</i>

52:03.320 --> 52:06.560
<i>-[Yeva continues chanting]</i>
<i>-[indistinct whispering]</i>

52:07.240 --> 52:10.000
<i>[Yeva's chant echoes]</i>

52:12.320 --> 52:13.400
<i>[screeches]</i>

52:14.120 --> 52:17.400
<i>[Lenore] </i>Take this to Merlin.
It's all that matters now.

52:17.480 --> 52:19.040
<i>[wind howling]</i>

52:19.560 --> 52:20.680
<i>[Lenore] </i>Run!

52:22.840 --> 52:24.720
<i>Papa! Don't go.</i>

52:24.800 --> 52:27.200
<i>You've brought darkness to this family,</i>
<i>Nimue.</i>

52:27.280 --> 52:29.520
<i>Jonah, she's your daughter. Do something.</i>

52:29.600 --> 52:30.680
<i>You are cursed.</i>

52:30.760 --> 52:34.040
<i>I'll fix it, Papa. I'll take the medicine.</i>
<i>I won't complain.</i>

52:34.640 --> 52:36.200
<i>It's in your blood, child.</i>

52:39.840 --> 52:41.360
<i>Ask your mother the reason...</i>

52:42.520 --> 52:43.720
<i>...I will not say it.</i>

52:48.960 --> 52:51.720
<i>Papa, I'm sorry. Come back!</i>

52:52.520 --> 52:53.920
<i>Please come back!</i>

52:54.960 --> 52:56.800
<i>[indistinct whispering]</i>

52:59.240 --> 53:00.720
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

53:07.440 --> 53:08.320
<i>[gasps]</i>

53:16.800 --> 53:17.680
<i>You're him.</i>

53:19.840 --> 53:20.800
<i>You're Merlin.</i>

53:26.000 --> 53:27.640
<i>And you're the Wolf-Blood Witch.</i>

53:29.000 --> 53:31.280
<i>Dreaded wielder of the Devil's Tooth.</i>

53:31.960 --> 53:33.680
<i>-You're making fun of me.</i>
<i>-No.</i>

53:36.360 --> 53:38.720
<i>But you're playing a dangerous game,</i>
<i>young lady.</i>

53:38.800 --> 53:40.480
<i>You think this is a game?</i>

53:40.560 --> 53:42.000
<i>[thunder cracking]</i>

53:50.600 --> 53:52.320
<i>What's your connection to this place?</i>

53:52.800 --> 53:53.800
<i>Why do you ask?</i>

53:54.560 --> 53:56.840
<i>The Between has found</i>
<i>a common ground for us.</i>

53:57.920 --> 53:59.760
<i>One we must both share in memory.</i>

54:00.720 --> 54:04.600
<i>Otherwise, we'd be in</i> <i>an ordinary room</i>
<i>or field, not here.</i>

54:05.800 --> 54:06.840
<i>I'm Sky Folk.</i>

54:07.600 --> 54:08.640
<i>This is my home.</i>

54:13.120 --> 54:15.200
<i>And this temple is where my mother died.</i>

54:18.480 --> 54:20.640
<i>-You're the daughter of Lenore?</i>
<i>-I am.</i>

54:21.640 --> 54:22.960
<i>She gave you the sword.</i>

54:23.040 --> 54:23.920
<i>Yes.</i>

54:25.760 --> 54:28.600
<i>And asked me with her dying breath</i>
<i>to bring the sword to you.</i>

54:30.080 --> 54:31.120
<i>You knew her?</i>

54:33.360 --> 54:34.640
<i>I did, yes.</i>

54:35.640 --> 54:38.280
<i>And, uh, her instructions to you</i>
<i>were very wise.</i>

54:38.360 --> 54:39.880
<i>-Look at me, Merlin.</i>
<i>-No, I'm sorry, I--</i>

54:39.960 --> 54:40.800
<i>Look at me.</i>

54:44.200 --> 54:45.280
<i>What do you see?</i>

54:46.240 --> 54:47.360
<i>You have her eyes.</i>

54:48.800 --> 54:49.760
<i>Anything else?</i>

54:51.200 --> 54:52.720
<i>What... what name were you given?</i>

54:52.800 --> 54:53.720
<i>Nimue.</i>

54:54.520 --> 54:55.440
<i>[Merlin] Nimue.</i>

54:57.520 --> 54:59.200
<i>That is indeed a beautiful name.</i>

55:00.440 --> 55:02.800
<i>I've been asking myself, "Why you?</i>

55:08.000 --> 55:10.360
<i>Why did she ask me</i>
<i>to bring the sword to you?"</i>

55:11.600 --> 55:12.440
<i>[gasps quietly]</i>

55:13.040 --> 55:14.240
<i>And what's your answer?</i>

55:16.160 --> 55:17.080
<i>Because...</i>

55:21.000 --> 55:22.200
<i>you're my father.</i>

55:23.160 --> 55:24.120
<i>[gasps]</i>

55:24.200 --> 55:25.320
<i>[gasps]</i>

55:27.840 --> 55:29.480
<i>[dramatic music plays]</i>

56:47.320 --> 56:48.360
<i>[music ends]</i>
